               <p>MR. PHILLIPS conducted the prosecution.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18330411-185-person1374">
                  THOMAS 
                  COLLINS
               <interp inst="t18330411-185-person1374" type="surname" value="COLLINS"></interp>
